## Provided configurations

This library provides the following configurations:

- [basic](./basic.mjs): Use this for casual js/typescript projects.
- [expo](./expo.mjs): Use this for React Native or Expo projects.
- [next](./next.mjs): Use this for Next.js projects.
- [node](./node.mjs): Use this for Node.js projects.
- [nx](./nx.mjs): Use this in the default NX Workspace Config.
